Class AccessPatternCondition

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.entities.AccessPatternCondition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IReferenceAware

    @Entity
public class AccessPatternCondition
extends java.lang.Object
implements IReferenceAware
    This class represents an auth pattern condition. It contains a list of auth pattern condition properties, a condition name and implements the ICondition interface.
